## Sample Code

```python
import pandas as pd

data = {
    "Product": ["Laptop", "Phone", "Tablet", "Laptop", "Phone"],
    "Sales": [50000, 30000, 20000, 45000, 25000]
}

df = pd.DataFrame(data)

total_sales = df["Sales"].sum()
print("Total Sales:", total_sales)


